FBIS4-8712 "dreeu074_y_94012" FBIS-EEU-94-074 Daily Report 15 Apr 1994 YUGOSLAVIA Montenegro Journalists' Accreditation Not To Be Withdrawn Journalists' Accreditation Not To Be Withdrawn LD1504175894 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in Serbo-Croatian 1500 GMT 15 Apr 94 LD1504175894 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network Serbo-Croatian BFN [Text] Unlike the Belgrade authorities, Montenegro will not withdraw accreditation from foreign journalists, said Information Minister Bozidar Jarebic. He added this action was mostly to the detriment of those who withdrew accreditation. There are many other ways of reaching agreements with journalists. That way Serbia finally showed that isolation was its permanent political choice.
